#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-archivemailagent; is an Akonadi agent which allows to archive mail "
"folders automatically."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-archivemailagent; je agent Akonadi, ki omogoča samodejno arhiviranje "
"poštnih map."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &i18n-archivemailagent;"
msgstr "Uporaba &i18n-archivemailagent;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Automatic "
"Archiving...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice><action> in &kmail;'s reader window "
"to open a dialog to set up automatic archiving of mail folders.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"samodejno arhiviranje ...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice><action> v oknu "
"bralnika &kmail;, da odprete pogovorno okno za nastavitev samodejnega "
"arhiviranja pošte mape.</action>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a powerful tool that can be used to assist in backing up your email. "
"To use this, click the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> button, and the "
"<guilabel>Add Archive Mail</guilabel> dialog will pop up."
msgstr ""
"To je zmogljivo orodje, ki vam lahko pomaga pri varnostnem kopiranju vaše e-"
"pošte. Če želite to uporabiti, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Dodaj...</guibutton> "
"in pojavilo se bo pogovorno okno <guilabel>Dodaj arhivsko pošto</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Add Archive Mail dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno Dodaj arhivsko pošto</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Add Archive Mail dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno Dodaj arhivsko pošto</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Add Archive Mail dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pogovorno okno Dodaj arhivsko pošto</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "First select the folder you would like to archive."
msgstr "Najprej izberite mapo, ki jo želite arhivirati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the format you would like to save it in. &eg; <literal role="
"\"extension\">.tar.bz2</literal> in the drop down list. The archive filename "
"will consist of the prefix <userinput>Archive_</userinput>, the path of the "
"selected folder in &kmail;'s folder list, the date in format <userinput>year-"
"month-day</userinput> and the selected file extension &eg; "
"<filename>Archive_Local Folder_inbox_2019-09-03.tar.bz2</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite obliko, v kateri jo želite shraniti. &eg; <literal role=\"extension"
"\">.tar.bz2</literal> na spustnem seznamu. Ime arhivske datoteke bo "
"sestavljeno iz predpone <userinput>Arhiv_</userinput>, poti izbrane mape na "
"seznamu map &kmail;, datuma v obliki <userinput>leto-mesec-dan</userinput> "
"in izbranega pripona datoteke &eg; <filename>Archive_Local "
"Folder_Inbox_2019-09-03.tar.bz2</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default <guilabel>Archive all subfolders</guilabel> is enabled. Uncheck "
"this if you only want the parent folder archived."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je omogočeno <guilabel>Arhiviraj vse podmape</guilabel>. Počistite "
"to polje, če želite arhivirati samo nadrejeno mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can type in the location you would like to save your archive, or click "
"the <guibutton>Open File Dialog</guibutton> button to select the folder."
msgstr ""
"Vnesete lahko mesto, kamor želite shraniti svoj arhiv, ali kliknete gumb "
"<guibutton>Odpri pogovorno okno datoteke</guibutton>, da izberete mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select how often you wish to backup through the dropdown menus next to "
"<guilabel>Backup each:</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"V spustnih menijih poleg <guilabel>Varnostno kopiraj vsako:</guilabel> "
"izberite, kako pogosto želite varnostno kopirati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are limited on drive space you will want to set a limit on "
"<guilabel>Maximum number of archive:</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Če imate omejen prostor na disku, boste želeli nastaviti omejitev "
"<guilabel>Največje število arhivov:</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have added or modified an archive job it will be executed "
"automatically after closing the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če ste dodali ali spremenili arhivsko opravilo, se bo samodejno izvršilo po "
"zaprtju pogovornega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have already added mail archive jobs the <guilabel>Configure Archive "
"Mail Agent</guilabel> dialog will list and allow to modify them."
msgstr ""
"Če ste že dodali poštna arhivska opravila, bo prikazano pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Konfiguriraj arhivskega poštnega agenta</guilabel> in omogočilo "
"njihovo spreminjanje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configure Archive Mail Agent</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfigurirajte arhivskega poštnega agenta</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure Archive Mail Agent</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguriraj arhivskega poštnega agenta</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Configure Archive Mail Agent</para>"
msgstr "<para>Konfigurirajte arhivskega poštnega agenta</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the checkbox at the left of each entry in the list to enable or "
"disable archiving of this job."
msgstr ""
"S potrditvenim poljem na levi strani vsakega vnosa na seznamu lahko "
"omogočite ali onemogočite arhiviranje tega posla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to access this configurational dialog any time later using "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kmail;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> then select the <guilabel>Plugins</guilabel> page "
"in &kmail; main window and pressing the configuration button against the "
"<guilabel>Archive Mail Agent</guilabel> item."
msgstr ""
"Do tega konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna lahko dostopate kadar koli "
"pozneje z uporabo <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kmail;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> nato "
"izberite <guilabel>Vtičniki</guilabel > stran v &kmail; glavno okno in "
"pritisnite gumb za konfiguracijo proti elementu <guilabel>Arhivski poštni "
"agent</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the context menu launched with a &RMB; click on an archive job you can "
"open the folder containing the archives or start the archive job "
"immediately. This will overwrite an existing archive created earlier at the "
"same day without notification."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo kontekstnega menija, ki ga zaženete z &RMB; kliknite na arhivsko "
"opravilo, lahko odprete mapo z arhivi ali takoj začnete arhivsko opravilo. "
"To bo prepisalo obstoječi arhiv, ustvarjen prej na isti dan brez obvestila."

